<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>CohabiSafe - Benefits for Renters</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css"> <!-- Use main styles for consistency -->
    <style>
        /* Override/Specific styles for this landing page if needed, otherwise reuse main css */
        body { background-color: var(--bg-color); }
        .marketing-header { text-align: center; padding: 60px 20px; background: white; }
        .marketing-header h1 { color: var(--primary-blue); font-size: 2.5rem; }
        .marketing-grid { max-width: 900px; margin: 40px auto; display: grid; gap: 20px; padding: 0 20px; }
        .benefit-card { 
            background: white; 
            padding: 30px; 
            border-radius: 12px; 
            border-left: 6px solid var(--primary-green); 
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }
        .benefit-card h2 { color: var(--text-dark); font-size: 1.5rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }
        .benefit-card p { color: var(--text-light); font-size: 1.1rem; margin-top: 10px; }
        .cta-container { text-align: center; margin: 60px 0; }
        .btn-massive { 
            background: var(--accent-orange); 
            color: white; 
            padding: 20px 50px; 
            font-size: 1.5rem; 
            border-radius: 50px; 
            font-weight: bold; 
            text-decoration: none; 
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(255, 149, 0, 0.3);
            transition: transform 0.2s;
        }
        .btn-massive:hover { transform: scale(1.05); }
    </style>
    <!-- Font Awesome -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body>
    
    <!-- Simple Nav for continuity -->
    <nav class="navbar">
        <div class="nav-content">
            <a href="/"><img src="/images/logo.jpg" alt="CohabiSafe Logo" class="logo"></a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <header class="marketing-header">
        <h1>Your Safe Start as a Renter</h1>
        <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; max-width: 600px; margin: 20px auto; color: #666;">
            Discover how we make finding the perfect roommate and home effortless and secure.
        </p>
    </header>
    
    <section class="marketing-grid">
        <div class="benefit-card">
            <h2><i class="fas fa-id-card-alt" style="color: var(--primary-blue);"></i> STAY SAFE</h2>
            <p><strong>Only strict identity-verified, background, and credit-checked participants</strong> are allowed in our network. We provide full matching support so you never have to worry about who you're meeting.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="benefit-card">
            <h2><i class="fas fa-user-friends" style="color: var(--accent-orange);"></i> SAVE MONEY AND MAKE FRIENDS</h2>
            <p>Our <strong>AI-powered personality matching</strong> connects you with roommates and landlords who truly click. Speed up your search with virtual room tours and find your people fast.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="benefit-card">
            <h2><i class="fas fa-suitcase-rolling" style="color: var(--primary-green);"></i> TEMPORARY ARRANGEMENTS</h2>
            <p>Looking for something short-term? Our <strong>relationship-driven cohabitation options</strong> let you experiment safely with flexible leases and verified hosts.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="benefit-card">
            <h2><i class="fas fa-check-circle" style="color: var(--primary-blue);"></i> PEACE OF MIND</h2>
            <p>With 24/7 support, secure data handling, and community guidelines, we ensure a safe experience from your first click to move-in day.</p>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <div class="cta-container">
        <a href="/account-setup" class="btn-massive">Create Free Account</a>
        <p style="margin-top: 20px; color: #888;">Takes less than 2 minutes.</p>
    </div>
    
    <footer>
        <div class="footer-bottom" style="background: #f4f7f9; color: #888; border: none;">
            <p>&copy; 2025 CohabiSafe. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>